Package Assets

Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • city.cs.engine.Body
      • city.cs.engine.DynamicBody
        • city.cs.engine.Walker
          • Assets.Person
  • public class Person
extends city.cs.engine.Walker
    A walker class that can flip its BodyImage horizontally to correctly position the image's direction. The walker class can move, has getters and setters for health and score. When another class (dynamic body or walker) collides with Person, a hit sound can be made.
